data.description: NO HOA! This property is a 3 bedroom, 2 bath home and could be a starter home or an investment property. This home has wood cabinets, ceiling fans throught the home, nice sized yard with a privacy fence and a covered patio. The home is located in the established subdivision of Brauns Farm with No Home Owners Association and minutes away from 1604, Shops, Restaurants and Helotes, TX.
